response.overview: Filmed live on the Nile Stage at Rotterdamâ€™s legendary Ahoy arena on 10 July 2009, this recording documents Duffy during the height of the "Rockferry" phenomenon. Fresh from winning a Grammy and three BRIT Awards, the singer delivers a defining set of soul, blending 1960s nostalgia with modern pop sensibilities, and culminating in her 2008 chart-topper 'Mercy'.  For over 15 years, this footage remained in the Dutch public broadcast vaults. Released in 2025, it serves as a poignant time capsule of a rising star who would shortly retreat from the public eye.
